em.\r\n\r\nWe analyze the sources of data and integrate them into the Hadoop cluster.\r\n\r\nWe implement appropriate tools to store, manipulate, visualize and produce strategic analyzes.\r\n\r\nWe can inject the results of your analysis to compare to other assumptions , we can extract and distribute them in different formats.\r\n<div align=\"center\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-581\" src=\"/en/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/integration_en.png\" alt=\"integration_en\" width=\"1083\" height=\"462\" /></div>\r\nWhatever your project , Hadoop integrates seamlessly into your environment because we are implementing the best market practices in terms of architecture.\r\n<div align=\"center\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-579\" src=\"/en/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/architecture_en.png\" alt=\"architecture_en\" width=\"839\" height=\"596\" /></div>','Integration','','publish','closed','closed','','integration','','','2015-12-06 00:40:43','2015-12-05 23:40:43','',2,'/en/?page_id=27',0,'page','',0),(30,1,'2015-10-05 12:22:12','2015-10-05 11:22:12','An issue that meets the constraints of data volume, velocity processing, variety of formats and sources and requires impeccable quality is determined by the Big Data technology.\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[virtual_slide_box id=\"1\"]</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nA Hadoop cluster secures the data volume and is expandable dynamic and instantaneous.\r\n\r\nThe algorithm Map / Reduce cluster allows to exploit the power calculation : it breaks up data into packets, optimizes the distribution through the cluster, compile the results.\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[virtual_slide_box id=\"2\"]</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nThe exploitation and analysis of system logs are used to correlate the anomalies systems security vulnerabilities .\r\n\r\nUsing a simple internet browser on any medium, analysis of results is done in real time regardless of the amount or selection of filters applied to the data.\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[virtual_slide_box id=\"3\"]</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nThe storage capacity and computing power used to encode hundreds of videos in different formats in record time .\r\n\r\nThe combination of data using metadata categorizes and simultaneously index this diversity of information.\r\n\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>[virtual_slide_box id=\"4\"]</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<div>\r\n\r\nBig Data enables reliable data by detecting unexpected peaks of activity, unusual .\r\n\r\nThe detection of abnormal situations is by the expression of explicit rules or by integrating statistical models and self-learning tools.\r\n<div></div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<blockquote>Once one of these issues can only be resolved by a conventional information system, the solution lies in implementing a Big Data platform in your environment.</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"wp-image-373 alignleft\" src=\"/en/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/gears.png\" alt=\"gears\" width=\"111\" height=\"71\" />The effectiveness of Big Data platforms is demonstrated.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The largest existing companies such as Google, Facebook, Yahoo! were the pioneers in this field.</p>\r\nThey used data for their services to analyze consumer needs in order to develop targeted Internet advertising.\r\n\r\nWe now know where they are, their reputation and their financial power.\r\n\r\nEvery business, <u> whatever its sector</u>, can benefit from this technology and realize its capital data to implement the business strategy of its own.','Big Data','','publish','closed','closed','','big-data','','','2015-12-03 12:51:28','2015-12-03 11:51:28','',0,'/en/?page_id=30',0,'page','',0),(31,1,'2015-10-05 12:22:12','2015-10-05 11:22:12',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','31','','','2015-10-17 12:14:29','2015-10-17 11:14:29','',0,'/en/index.php/2015/10/05/31/',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(706,1,'